14:10.017 --> 14:12.085
what are you gonna do
with all those feelings?

14:12.085 --> 14:14.087
(Cell phone ringing)

14:14.087 --> 14:15.122
Ah.

14:15.122 --> 14:17.124
Oh, tell him I said hi.

14:17.124 --> 14:20.027
Hey, Patrick. What's up?
What do you know about
congressman Charles Watley?

14:20.027 --> 14:24.031
He voted against Simon's bio-fuel
a few years back.

14:24.031 --> 14:26.066
