17:30.050 --> 17:32.119
And you're gonna do it?
Why the hell wouldn't I?

17:32.119 --> 17:35.055
You just got married
to Andrea.

17:35.055 --> 17:38.058
Andrea's got nothing
to do with this.
Unbelievable.

17:38.058 --> 17:39.126
