You're comparing me

20:34.629 --> 20:36.698
to your precious little Lisa.
No, no, no.

20:36.698 --> 20:39.701
Uh-huh. You are.
Well, I got news for you, pal.

20:39.701 --> 20:42.637
Your precious little Lisa stole
