Simple relationship in my life

20:53.715 --> 20:58.653
about me being my best
for someone else.

20:58.653 --> 21:01.656
And if that means it's with
someone who wears a diaper

21:01.656 --> 21:03.591
and doesn't talk English,

21:03.591 --> 21:06.628
then so be it.
(Engine clanks)

21:06.628 --> 21:09.631
(Sputtering)

21:12.600 --> 21:13.668
Damn it.

21:13.668 --> 21:15.603
