21:15.603 --> 21:16.638
(Sighs)

21:16.638 --> 21:19.674
Karen's sincerity
killed the car.

21:21.676 --> 21:22.710
(Sighs)

21:22.710 --> 21:24.646
Sorry.

21:27.715 --> 21:29.651
I am tired.

21:31.686 --> 21:33.688
My toe hurts.

21:33.688 --> 21:36.658
(Patrick)
It's dead in the water, dad.

21:36.658 --> 21:38.660
I went to see Watley,
and quite frankly,

21:38.660 --> 21:41.596
