anybody, ever--anyone.

21:47.702 --> 21:51.639
I don't want to go back to
Watley and push him on this.

21:51.639 --> 21:54.642
This is your problem.
You caused it. You fix it.

21:54.642 --> 21:58.713
Patrick, I very rarely
ask you to do anything.

21:58.713 --> 22:01.649
This is for the family,
for the company.

22:01.649 --> 22:04.686
You go back to Mr. Watley...

22:04.686 --> 22:07.655
And you get it done.

22:09.691 --> 22:11.726
Right, dad.

22:11.726 --> 22:15.697
You've never squeezed anybody.

22:15.697 --> 22:18.600
