22:52.700 --> 22:54.702
For what?
Don't you see?

22:54.702 --> 22:57.705
He's fed you information,
and now he's gonna sit back

22:57.705 --> 23:00.642
and see what you're gonna
do with it.

23:00.642 --> 23:03.678
