do something pretty bad.

23:09.684 --> 23:11.686
To who?

23:11.686 --> 23:13.655
Me.

23:16.724 --> 23:19.694
Lisa, it's me.

23:19.694 --> 23:23.598
What, Nick?
I'm at a motel
just outside of D. C.,

23:23.598 --> 23:25.667
and I will be there in
the morning to pick up Kiki.

23:25.667 --> 23:28.670
I told you... I told you I would
get her back to you on Monday.

23:28.670 --> 23:31.673
Why did you come down here?
